727077f-a.text:
(1)
Jamaica Ave., north side, opposite 205th Street, showing the Samuel Cozine house of 1896.  Bergen Brothers owned it in 1860; A.S. Bergen in 1891.  One Silverman had his real estate office here in 1923.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) and (3)
The same, showing the same house with the one story wing removed.

May 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(4)
The same, showing it in a dilapidated state, at the N.W. corner of 199th Street and Jamaica Ave.

April 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
